you want to marry.

107
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:52,833
I'm sorry.

108
00:08:55,666 --> 00:08:56,833
I'm a bit tired.

109
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,750
Go home first.

110
00:09:01,291 --> 00:09:02,625
K is dying.

111
00:09:11,958 --> 00:09:13,500
So please,

112
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,541
I'm begging you,

113
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,875
