with all your heart and soul.

123
00:10:06,458 --> 00:10:07,833
<i>It's a very blissful thing.</i>

124
00:10:11,375 --> 00:10:13,166
<i>Anyway, loving someone that way</i>

125
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:14,666
