126
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:20,250
<i>Due to possible relationship disputes,</i>

127
00:10:20,333 --> 00:10:23,083
<i>the famous musician Wang Po-han
was stabbed a few days ago.</i>

128
00:10:23,166 --> 00:10:24,458
