182
00:14:42,416 --> 00:14:43,416
<i>Po-han.</i>

183
00:14:44,708 --> 00:14:46,208
<i>Thank you for everything.</i>

184
00:14:49,666 --> 00:14:51,958
<i>But the pain of losing Ke-le</i>

185
00:14:53,583 --> 00:14:55,666
