186
00:14:58,166 --> 00:15:01,125
<i>-Sometimes, missing him</i>
-Kids, come back. Hurry up.

187
00:15:01,208 --> 00:15:04,958
<i>-makes me feel like I can't even breathe.</i>
-Be careful.

188
00:15:05,958 --> 00:15:08,333
-Rock paper scissors!
-Rock paper scissors!

189
00:15:08,416 --> 00:15:11,375
<i>I can't stop missing Ke-le at all.</i>

190
00:15:12,041 --> 00:15:12,958
<i>Come here.</i>

191
00:15:20,208 --> 00:15:21,500
<i>I'm often wondering</i>

192
00:15:22,333 --> 00:15:25,250
<i>if he came back to see me.</i>

193
00:15:27,583 --> 00:15:29,208
<i>I'd tell him,</i>

194
00:15:30,458 --> 00:15:31,875
<i>"Don't cry, Ke-le.</i>

195
00:15:32,583 --> 00:15:33,750
<i>Go happily</i>

196
00:15:34,416 --> 00:15:36,250
<i>to the place
where there's no sickness and pain.</i>

197
00:15:37,375 --> 00:15:38,666
<i>Wait for me.</i>

198
00:15:40,541 --> 00:15:44,375
<i>Save your tears for me."</i>

199
00:15:48,916 --> 00:15:49,875
<i>Po-han,</i>

200
00:15:50,375 --> 00:15:51,416
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

201
00:15:53,625 --> 00:15:54,958
<i>I'm not confident</i>

202
00:15:55,041 --> 00:15:56,708
<i>to be able to say goodbye.</i>

203
00:16:00,416 --> 00:16:02,208
<i>I don't know</i>

204
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,875
<i>how to let go of my sadness</i>

205
00:16:07,208 --> 00:16:08,708
<i>and get used to goodbyes.</i>

206
00:16:11,833 --> 00:16:14,791
<i>I can't keep pretending
to be strong anymore.</i>

207
00:16:15,791 --> 00:16:17,875
<i>I have no reason to stay here either.</i>

208
00:16:20,875 --> 00:16:22,791
AN YI-CHI

209
00:16:22,875 --> 00:16:24,250
<i>Please take care of yourself.</i>

210
00:16:27,625 --> 00:16:29,000
<i>Please forgive me.</i>

